Grammy award-winning act, Wizkid has been struck with overloads of sweetness he’s been receiving in Lagos. In January, Wizkid confessed his love for the ‘Centre of Excellence. He also opened up on why he loves the state. The “Blessed” singer posted fun videos as well as photos from a club hangout with the likes of Buju, Wande Coal, Bella Shmurda and Nollywood actress, Osas Ighodaro via his Snapchat story. One particular video had the caption: “I Love Lagos.”   Rihanna will be a ‘good mum’, father ecstatic over pregnancy     My father wanted me to study Law — Comedian Oga Sabinus     Don’t be like me, Tonto Dikeh advises fans   - Advertisement - In the video that followed, Big Wiz declared he loves Lagos because of the many fun activities from the mad parties and of course, the women. He added that it is one of the many reasons he spends more time in Lagos than in the United Kingdom. Now, in another Snapchat story, the father of three further affirmed his love for the metropolitan city wondered why it stays sweet all day…. every day. “Lagos!! Why you sweet like this?” he queried.